  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil or vegan butter in a wok over medium-high heat.",
    "Add Sichuan peppercorns and minced garlic to the hot oil. Stir for about 30 seconds until fragrant.",
    "Add sliced green onions, broccoli florets, and carrots to the wok. Mix well with the spices.",
    "Pour soy sauce evenly into the stir-fry mixture and mix thoroughly.",
    "Stir-fry everything for about 5-7 minutes or until vegetables are tender but still a little crisp.",
    "If desired, sprinkle crushed peanuts on top before serving."
